---
// Problems.astro — 3-up grid of status-quo pain points.
---
<section class="section" style="background:var(--canvas)">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">The status quo</div>
      <h2 class="display-lg">Mobile maintenance is a tax you keep paying.</h2>
      <p>Every sprint a third of the team's velocity disappears into the same shape of work. Three reasons it stays that way:</p>
    </div>
    <div class="problems-grid">

      <article class="feature-card reveal">
        <span class="icon-tile" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4" />
            <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="title-md">Tests get skipped.</h3>
        <p>Engineers trust the stacktrace plus the migration doc and ship without an end-to-end run. The bug survives the release.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="feature-card reveal">
        <span class="icon-tile" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="4" rx="1" />
            <rect x="3" y="10" width="18" height="4" rx="1" />
            <rect x="3" y="16" width="18" height="4" rx="1" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="title-md">Unfixable bugs pile up.</h3>
        <p>Dependency races, old-hardware crashes, intermittent failures — most never get filed upstream. They just sit in the dashboard.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="feature-card reveal">
        <span class="icon-tile" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3 class="title-md">Maintenance delays releases.</h3>
        <p>Last-minute QA finds a missing null check. Eng gets pulled back in. The exciting new feature ships next sprint instead.</p>
      </article>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
